            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-403] ReReadMetadataCb is not executed in the thread responsible for that ledger</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-403</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Attached a patch to execute the callback in bk.mainWorkerPool instead of on the zookeeper thread.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12607370">BOOKKEEPER-403</key>
            <summary>ReReadMetadataCb is not executed in the thread responsible for that ledger</summary>
